▍推荐人：LUKEWONG</p><blockquote><p>这两个电台是我在英语交流圈里经常推荐的电台，电台主持人口语很纯正，每一期教学的口语非常实用。</p></blockquote><h2 style=\"color: #db4c55; text-align: center;\">▽</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>聆听美国</strong></p><p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7330\" src=\"http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93943.jpg\" alt=\"ira-glass-lead-tal-promo\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93943-444x333.jpg 444w, http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93943.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p><p>▍名称：<a href=\"https://www.thisamericanlife.org/\" target=\"_blank\">This American Life</a><br />
▍推荐人：jingyi｜Programmer</p><p>This American Life 是一个由 WBEZ 制作，并由艾拉·格拉斯主持的电台节目。它的主要内容分类为非虚构新闻，但有时也会包含随笔、回忆录、现场录音及短篇小说等。</p><h2 style=\"color: #db4c55; text-align: center;\">▽</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Locked on NBA</strong></p><p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-7333\" src=\"http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/27235.jpg\" alt=\"lockedonlakers\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" srcset=\"http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/27235-500x333.jpg 500w, http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/27235.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></p><p>▍名称：<a href=\"https://audioboom.com/channel/locked-on-lakers\" target=\"_blank\">Locked on Lakers</a><br />
▍推荐人：Joshua｜投资人</p><p>一档专门报道 NBA 洛杉矶湖人队新闻的播客节目，从交易流言、赛事播报到队内新闻，湖人球迷推荐播客，更新还很勤快。</p><h2 style=\"color: #db4c55; text-align: center;\">▽</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>科学美国人 60s 科学</strong></p><p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-7328\" src=\"http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93395-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"21264210.1371159922\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93395-150x150.jpg 150w, http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93395-333x333.jpg 333w, http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93395-768x768.jpg 768w, http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93395-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, http://liqi.io/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/93395.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></p><p>▍名称：<a href=\"https://www.scientificamerican.com/podcast/60-second-science/\" target=\"_blank\">60-Second Science</a><br />
